      <reaction compartment="compartment_7660" fast="false" id="reaction_997263" metaid="metaid_134" name="JMJD1C demethylates H3K9 mono- and di-methylation" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">JMJD1C specifically demethylates histone H3K9 mono- and di-methylation, thereby mediating transcriptional activation.</p>
