      <reaction compartment="compartment_7660" fast="false" id="reaction_994038" metaid="metaid_143" name="IRF2 binds the promoters of Interferon alpha and beta" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Interferon regulatory factor 2 (IRF-2) represses the action of IRF-1 on type I interferon genes (Harada et al, 1989, 1990; Palombella and Maniatis, 1992) by competing with IRF-1 for binding at the PRDI site.</p>
        </notes>
        <annotation>
          <rdf:RDF xmlns:rdf="http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:vCard="http://www.w3.org/2001/vcard-rdf/3.0#" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:bqbiol="http://biomodels.net/biology-qualifiers/">
