      <reaction compartment="compartment_70101" fast="false" id="reaction_2267372" metaid="metaid_148" name="ITPK1 converts Ins-1,3,4-P3 to Ins-1,3,4,6-P4" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Inositol-tetrakisphosphate 1-kinase (ITPK1) phosphorylates Ins(1,3,4)P3 on O-6 to form Ins(1,3,4,6)P4, an essential molecule in the hexakisphosphate (InsP6) pathway.</p>
